✈️ Flight Data Practice Scenarios
🟢 Easy Level

Find airports where more than 8% of flights are cancelled

Find airlines where more than 15% of flights are delayed (dep_delay > 0)

Find destinations where more than 10% of flights arrive late (>15 min)

Find months where more than 5% of flights are cancelled

Find days where more than 20% of flights depart late

🟡 Medium Level

Find airlines where average departure delay is greater than 25 minutes

Find destinations where less than 70% of flights arrive on time

Find routes (origin + destination) where more than 12% of flights are cancelled

Find aircraft (tailnum) where more than 30% of flights are delayed

Find days where average arrival delay is more than 30 minutes

🔴 Advanced Level

Find airports that have at least 100 flights AND more than 10% cancellations

Find airlines where more than 25% flights are delayed AND average delay > 20 min

Find routes where total flights > 50 AND more than 20% are late arrivals

Find months where on-time performance is below 65%

Find aircrafts that have at least 200 flights AND more than 40% delays

🔥 Challenging (Interview-style)

Find the top 5 airports with highest cancellation percentage

Find airlines where cancellation rate increased month-over-month

Find days where both departure AND arrival delays exceed 25%

Find routes where average delay is high but cancellation rate is low (<5%)

Find the airport with the most consistent on-time performance (lowest delay variance)
